snippet.title: A Little To The Left (Teaser Trailer)
snippet.description: A Little To The Left is a cozy puzzle game that has you sort, stack, and organize things into just the right spot. Discover curious logical arrangements of a person stuck at home with their mischievous cat in this playful and intuitive puzzler with 55+ satisfying messes to tidy.
